cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.IR 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of "cs.CL" (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing tasks such as argument labeling of explicit discourse relations. It may also belong to "cs.AI" (Artificial Intelligence) and "cs.LG" (Machine Learning) as it proposes a Long Short Term Memory (LSTM) based model for the task. Additionally, it could be categorized under "cs.NE" (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it uses neural networks for the task. Finally, it may also be classified under "cs.IR" (Information Retrieval) as argument labeling is a crucial task in information retrieval systems.
